      "content": "exactly. it feels like they're basically treating my living room like a lab. what's even scarier is how some of these devices could probably tell if I'm lying or if I'm hiding something just from my voice or movement patterns. if they're already doing this with light and temp, how far could they actually go with more advanced sensing? could they be using this to build a full psychological profile without us ever knowing?",
